01:15:42,480 --> 01:15:44,280
Ako se prije ne izgubi .

974
01:15:44,280 --> 01:15:46,480
Znam da je u blizini jezero.

975
01:15:46,681 --> 01:15:47,881
On osjeca to.

976
01:15:47,881 --> 01:15:50,601
Osjecajan.
Ako se uvalite u nevolje. . .

977
01:15:50,881 --> 01:15:53,481
. . .svakako me. . .
Nazovite novine.

978
01:15:55,081 --> 01:15:57,441
- Zelis kormilariti?
- Svakako.

979
01:15:57,482 --> 01:15:59,082
i si kapetan.

980
01:15:59,282 --> 01:16:01,122
Moras drzati smjer.

981
01:16:02,282 --> 01:16:03,722
Ravno naprijed .

982
01:16:13,923 --> 01:16:14,884
Izvoli .

983
01:16:15,403 --> 01:16:17,283
- Kako si?
- Dobro.

984
01:16:19,604 --> 01:16:21,404
Cijelo drustvo. Bok, Lenny.

985
01:16:21,404 --> 01:16:23,685
- 'Djenja, mama.
- Zabavi se.

986
01:16:24,405 --> 01:16:26,685
- Pozdravi mamu.
- Vidimo se!

987
01:16:55,608 --> 01:16:57,609
Nisam navikla da si tu.

988
01:17:01,009 --> 01:17:02,848
U redu je, Garrete.

989
01:17:05,209 --> 01:17:06,849
Lijepo je. . .

990
01:17:07,610 --> 01:17:09,810
. . . medju tvojim stvarima.

991
01:17:13,010 --> 01:17:14,891
Jesi li to ocekivao?

992
01:17:17,211 --> 01:17:18,691
Ugodno je.

993
01:17:38,213 --> 01:17:40,213
Cinis me samosvjesnom .

994
01:17:43,014 --> 01:17:44,533
Sto gledas?

995
01:17:45,413 --> 01:17:47,374
Theresu u njezinu domu.

996
01:17:51,414 --> 01:17:53,415
Obicna svakodnevna. . .

997
01:17:54,414 --> 01:17:55,975
. . .Theresa.

998
01:18:12,416 --> 01:18:13,776
Cekaj .

999
01:18:14,817 --> 01:18:16,537
Doista sam . . .

1000
01:18:16,617 --> 01:18:19,137
. . . htjela da ovo bude kako treba.

1001
01:18:20,217 --> 01:18:23,418
Htjela sam pospremiti sobu
i upaliti svijecu i . . .

1002
01:18:26,218 --> 01:18:28,218
I moram se istusirati .

1003
01:18:35,819 --> 01:18:37,339
Garrete, cekaj .

1004
01:20:15,830 --> 01:20:18,750
1, 2, 3. . .

1005
01:20:19,150 --> 01:20:20,751
. . .4, 5, 6!

1006
01:20:23,950 --> 01:20:25,751
- aj je bio dobar.
- Bojim se.

1007
01:20:25,751 --> 01:20:27,551
Ja se tako bojim .

1008
01:20:27,551 --> 01:20:29,311
Ovo je bilo jako.

1009
01:20:31,751 --> 01:20:33,992
Idem se istusirati . Napokon.

1010
01:20:37,753 --> 01:20:39,513
Cekaj . Samo. . .

1011
01:22:17,963 --> 01:22:20,003
Pronadjena Poruka U Boci

1012
01:22:20,364 --> 01:22:22,043
Draga Catherine

1013
01:22:23,364 --> 01:22:25,404
Neces vjerovati sto. . .

1014
01:22:30,564 --> 01:22:32,324
O, Boze, Garrete.

1015
01:22:32,965 --> 01:22:34,565
Otkud ti ovo?

1016
01:22:38,965 --> 01:22:40,165
Pronasla sam .

1017
01:22:40,165 --> 01:22:41,966
Kako to mislis, pronasla?

1018
01:22:41,966 --> 01:22:43,806
Pronasla na obali .

1019
01:22:44,966 --> 01:22:46,687
Garrete, cekaj .

1020
01:22:47,367 --> 01:22:49,127
Doslo je k meni .

1021
01:22:49,766 --> 01:22:51,567
Moras mi vjerovati .

1022
01:22:51,567 --> 01:22:53,167
Vjerovati ti?

1023
01:22:53,367 --> 01:22:56,807
Morala sam upoznati autora
toga. Morala sam upoznati tebe.

1024
01:22:57,567 --> 01:22:59,968
- Htjela sam ti prije reci .
- Kako si me mogla pronaci?

1025
01:22:59,968 --> 01:23:02,928
Pronasla sam sve poruke
i u njima tragove. . .

1026
01:23:04,768 --> 01:23:06,289
Sve poruke?

1027
01:23:08,369 --> 01:23:11,849
Sve su pronadjene. Ljudi su
procitali clanak i pisali nam .

1028
01:23:11,969 --> 01:23:14,369
Kunem se Bogom, kanila sam ti reci .

1029
01:23:14,369 --> 01:23:15,569
Garrete, cekaj .

1030
01:23:15,569 --> 01:23:17,010
Moram odavde.

1031
01:23:22,050 --> 01:23:23,051
Garrete, cekaj !

1032
01:23:23,290 --> 01:23:24,971
Zasto si to ucinila?

1033
01:23:25,970 --> 01:23:27,330
Zasto?!

1034
01:23:28,971 --> 01:23:30,851
Bila si znatizeljna?

1035
01:23:31,972 --> 01:23:34,972
- To je prokleto istrazivanje?
- Ne, zaljubljujem se u tebe!

1036
01:23:34,972 --> 01:23:37,932
Prvo u pisma, a kad sam
te upoznala, i u tebe!

1037
01:23:37,972 --> 01:23:40,132
I zao mi je! Bojala sam se!

1038
01:23:40,372 --> 01:23:43,292
Bojala sam se da cu te otjerati
kazem li ti !

1039
01:23:43,373 --> 01:23:45,332
Kao sto to sad cinim !

1040
01:23:46,373 --> 01:23:47,573
Cekaj !

1041
01:23:47,573 --> 01:23:49,373
Ma sto mislio o meni . . .

1042
01:23:49,373 --> 01:23:51,174
. . . ma sto se dogodilo, zelim da znas. . .

1043
01:23:51,174 --> 01:23:52,974
. . . koliko mi je stalo do tebe.

1044
01:23:52,974 --> 01:23:55,214
Ne bi trebalo biti vazno. . .

1045
01:23:55,374 --> 01:23:57,775
. . .sto nas je spojilo, Garrete.

1046
01:23:57,775 --> 01:24:00,694
Bacio sam ta pisma u more za nju,
ne za tebe!

1047
01:24:00,775 --> 01:24:02,575
Ne za tvoje prijatelje s posla!

1048
01:24:02,575 --> 01:24:03,775
Znam .

1049
01:24:03,775 --> 01:24:06,015
Svi su znali za mene, zar ne?

1050
01:24:06,775 --> 01:24:07,975
Sve o Catherine?

1051
01:24:07,975 --> 01:24:10,496
Ta su mi tri pisma promijenila zivot.

1052
01:24:12,176 --> 01:24:13,975
- Nisam htjela da to novine objave.
- Dva pisma.

1053
01:24:13,975 --> 01:24:17,336
- Moras mi vjerovati .
- Poslao sam dva pisma Catherine.

1054
01:24:19,376 --> 01:24:20,576
Molim?

1055
01:24:20,576 --> 01:24:22,657
Imam sva pisma. Sva tri .

1056
01:24:25,977 --> 01:24:27,857
Gdje je trece pismo?

1057
01:24:28,977 --> 01:24:30,737
U onoj je ladici?

1058
01:24:39,778 --> 01:24:41,259
Catherine?

1059
01:25:05,581 --> 01:25:07,742
Svim brodovima na moru. . .

1060
01:25:07,982 --> 01:25:09,822
. . .i svim lukama:

1061
01:25:10,382 --> 01:25:12,182
Mojoj obitelji. . .

1062
01:25:12,182 --> 01:25:14,583
. . .svim prij eljima i neznancima:

1063
01:25:14,583 --> 01:25:16,623
Ovo je poruka i molitva:

1064
01:25:18,183 --> 01:25:21,543
Poruka je da su me moja
putovanja naucila vaznoj istini.

1065
01:25:23,583 --> 01:25:26,384
Vec sam imala ono
sto svi drugi traze. . .

1066
01:25:26,584 --> 01:25:28,784
. . .a malo tko ikad nadje.

1067
01:25:28,984 --> 01:25:30,785
Jednu osobu koju sam. . .

1068
01:25:30,785 --> 01:25:33,024
. . .rodjena voljeti zauvijek.

1069
01:25:33,785 --> 01:25:36,345
Osobu poput mene, s Outer Banksa. . .

1070
01:25:37,985 --> 01:25:40,745
. . .i tajanstvenu poput modrog Atlantika.

1071
01:25:42,185 --> 01:25:44,586
Osobu prepunu jednostavnih blaga. . .

1072
01:25:44,586 --> 01:25:47,026
. . .kovaca svoje srece, samoukog.

1073
01:25:49,386 --> 01:25:51,546
Luku u kojoj sam uvijek doma.

1074
01:25:52,387 --> 01:25:54,467
Nikakvi zli vjetrovi. . .

1075
01:25:55,387 --> 01:25:58,748
. . .ni neka mala smrt ne
mogu unistiti tog covjeka.

1076
01:26:01,988 --> 01:26:05,228
Molim se da svatko na
svijtu upozna takvu ljubav. . .

1077
01:26:06,788 --> 01:26:08,749
. . .i da ga izlijeci.

1078
01:26:09,189 --> 01:26:12,549
Cuje li tko moju molitvu,
ponistit ce se svi grijesi...

1079
01:26:13,989 --> 01:26:16,269
. . .i sve za cime zalite. . .

1080
01:26:16,389 --> 01:26:18,630
. . .i nece vise biti gnjeva.

1081
01:26:19,990 --> 01:26:21,670
Molim te, Boze.

1082
01:26:22,390 --> 01:26:23,670
Amen.

1083
01:26:34,391 --> 01:26:36,791
Nikad nisam znao sto je napisala.

1084
01:26:39,192 --> 01:26:40,592
Ona. . .

1085
01:26:40,992 --> 01:26:43,712
. . .se poslije toga dana nije oporavila.

1086
01:26:45,793 --> 01:26:48,353
Osusio sam je. Pokusao je zagrijati .

1087
01:26:49,392 --> 01:26:51,393
Odveo sam je u bolnicu.

1088
01:26:52,993 --> 01:26:54,673
Ona nikad . . .

1089
01:26:58,394 --> 01:27:00,514
Umrla je tri dana poslije.

1090
01:27:03,195 --> 01:27:05,955
Stalno mislim da tog dana nije izasla. . .

1091
01:27:06,195 --> 01:27:08,155
Garrete, ona je znala.

1092
01:27:10,995 --> 01:27:12,556
Rekla je to.

1093
01:27:13,396 --> 01:27:16,835
" Ni mala smrt ne moze unistiti
tog covjeka. " Znala je.

1094
01:27:22,997 --> 01:27:24,516
Zelim . . .

1095
01:27:24,796 --> 01:27:26,597
. . .zadrzati ovo.

1096
01:28:34,284 --> 01:28:36,684
Oprosti . Bi li radije bila sama?

1097
01:28:43,886 --> 01:28:45,485
Je li nazvao?

1098
01:28:48,686 --> 01:28:50,806
No ostavila sam mu poruku.

1099
01:28:52,287 --> 01:28:54,287
Rekla sam da mi je zao.

1100
01:28:55,287 --> 01:28:57,487
I zamolila sam ga da nazove.

1101
01:28:58,888 --> 01:29:00,567
Pa onda i hoce.

1102
01:29:03,088 --> 01:29:04,968
Lina, sjecas se. . .

1103
01:29:06,088 --> 01:29:08,528
. . . na sto sam se uvijek zalila?

1104
01:29:09,088 --> 01:29:11,848
Svaki put kad sam ti plakala
zbog Davida?

1105
01:29:12,088 --> 01:29:13,568
Sjecas se?

1106
01:29:14,489 --> 01:29:16,449
Iskrenost. Povjerenje.

1107
01:29:21,090 --> 01:29:22,890
Tako sam se bojala.

1108
01:29:24,689 --> 01:29:26,170
Ja ne. . .

1109
01:29:27,090 --> 01:29:29,490
Zaljubljujem se u Garreta i . . .

1110
01:29:31,290 --> 01:29:33,091
Pola mozga govori mi :
" Kazi mu" . . .

1111
01:29:33,091 --> 01:29:35,371
. . .a druga polovica govori :

1112
01:29:37,292 --> 01:29:39,411
" Cekaj . Nece shvatiti .

1113
01:29:40,292 --> 01:29:41,492
Cekaj pravi trenutak.

1114
01:29:41,492 --> 01:29:43,732
Cekaj prave rijeci . " Znas?

1115
01:29:45,692 --> 01:29:47,732
Uprskala sam . Samo. . .

1116
01:29:48,093 --> 01:29:50,653
Ubila sam to postavsi ono sto mrzim :

1117
01:29:51,093 --> 01:29:52,293
Lazljivica.

1118
01:29:52,293 --> 01:29:54,013
Nisi lazljivica.

1119
01:29:54,693 --> 01:29:56,573
Ali za njega jesam .

1120
01:29:58,293 --> 01:30:01,173
I ne vjerujem da ce mi ikad
moci vjerovati .

1121
01:30:01,894 --> 01:30:04,294
Ne shvacas da svi imamo male lazi?

1122
01:30:04,294 --> 01:30:06,375
Male neizgovorene istine?

1123
01:30:07,295 --> 01:30:10,215
Moras vjerovati u to
da ce i on to shvatiti .

1124
01:30:13,295 --> 01:30:14,736
Ne znam .

1125
01:30:16,896 --> 01:30:18,856
Ne znam moze li on to.

1126
01:30:21,096 --> 01:30:24,617
Vidjela sam njegovu bol .
Drzao je njezino pismo i citao ga.

1127
01:30:25,896 --> 01:30:27,656
Vidjela sam . . .

1128
01:30:29,497 --> 01:30:31,537
. . .toliko boli i . . .

1129
01:30:32,497 --> 01:30:34,537
On je toliko voli, znas?

1130
01:30:37,898 --> 01:30:39,338
Ne znam .

1131
01:30:50,499 --> 01:30:53,940
Rekao si da ako ikad pozelim
nesto napisati za novine. . .

1132
01:32:13,628 --> 01:32:15,189
Ne salis se.

1133
01:32:17,229 --> 01:32:18,829
On je u tome?

1134
01:32:19,029 --> 01:32:20,309
Nije.

1135
01:32:20,829 --> 01:32:22,389
Druge price.

1136
01:32:22,629 --> 01:32:24,190
Dobre price.

1137
01:32:24,429 --> 01:32:26,230
Bilo je i vrijeme.

1138
01:32:28,630 --> 01:32:31,190
Kad ljude povrijedis, oni se zatvore.

1139
01:32:31,631 --> 01:32:33,470
Dok bol ne nestane?

1140
01:32:34,631 --> 01:32:36,071
Ne znam .

1141
01:32:36,431 --> 01:32:39,271
Mozda naucis to prihvatiti
kao i sve drugo.

1142
01:32:41,232 --> 01:32:43,832
Kako komadice cepa
u casi finog vina.

1143
01:32:44,831 --> 01:32:46,912
Ne zelis propustiti vino.

1144
01:32:47,232 --> 01:32:48,832
To je u ovome?

1145
01:32:49,632 --> 01:32:51,353
To o cepu u vinu?

1146
01:32:52,633 --> 01:32:53,833
Nije.

1147
01:32:53,833 --> 01:32:55,713
Dobro. Gadilo mi se.

1148
01:33:02,234 --> 01:33:05,114
Mozda svi mi pisemo
svoje zivotne price. . .

1149
01:33:05,834 --> 01:33:08,314
. . .izmisljajuci ih iz dana u dan.

1150
01:33:08,834 --> 01:33:12,515
No cini se da drugi imaju
zivote vec oblikovane i planirane. . .

1151
01:33:13,035 --> 01:33:14,915
. . .neizbjezne. . .

1152
01:33:15,435 --> 01:33:17,716
. . .savrsene poput kruznice.

1153
01:35:17,248 --> 01:35:18,648
Otvori.

1154
01:35:19,649 --> 01:35:21,009
Polako.

1155
01:35:26,250 --> 01:35:28,489
- Ovo je uzbudljivo.
- Jest.

1156
01:35:31,650 --> 01:35:34,050
Cudesno Putovanje
Izgubljen i pronadjen na moru

1157
01:35:34,050 --> 01:35:36,050
Prva stranica!
Sjajno!

1158
01:35:36,450 --> 01:35:37,651
Hvala, stari .

1159
01:35:37,651 --> 01:35:39,411
Mogu ga izrezati?

1160
01:35:39,450 --> 01:35:40,371
Svakako.

1161
01:35:42,091 --> 01:35:44,011
- Ovo je u redu?
- Sjajno.

1162
01:35:44,251 --> 01:35:46,211
Savrseno. Hvala.

1163
01:35:53,172 --> 01:35:54,373
Vasa posta.

1164
01:35:54,373 --> 01:35:55,573
Hvala.

1165
01:35:55,573 --> 01:35:57,133
I drugi put.

1166
01:36:13,575 --> 01:36:14,775
Draga heresa.

1167
01:36:14,775 --> 01:36:15,975
Mnogo sam razmisljao o tebi .

1168
01:36:15,975 --> 01:36:18,375
Da nije bilo tebe, ne bih znao
Catherineine posljednje rijeci .

1169
01:36:18,375 --> 01:36:20,775
Mislim da sam sve sto osjecam
stavio u ovaj brod .

1170
01:36:20,775 --> 01:36:22,575
Porinut cu ga 25-og .

1171
01:36:22,575 --> 01:36:25,736
Nadam se da ces ga uskoro vidjeti .
Voli te Garret.

1172
01:36:27,976 --> 01:36:29,336
Lijepo.

1173
01:36:29,777 --> 01:36:31,977
Svidja mi se sto si ucinila.

1174
01:36:32,777 --> 01:36:35,177
- Veoma minimalisticki .
- Lijepo od vas sto ste svratili .

1175
01:36:35,177 --> 01:36:38,777
Da, donosim darove za tvoj
novi ured u telefonskoj govornici .

1176
01:36:39,378 --> 01:36:41,177
- Smijem objesiti?
-Tako slatko.

1177
01:36:41,177 --> 01:36:42,498
Znam .

1178
01:36:49,578 --> 01:36:51,779
Nikad neces pogoditi tko je.

1179
01:36:56,179 --> 01:36:57,939
Doimas se sretno.

1180
01:36:57,979 --> 01:36:59,500
Sve u redu?

1181
01:37:03,380 --> 01:37:04,660
Aha.

1182
01:37:06,381 --> 01:37:07,741
Smijem?

1183
01:37:11,781 --> 01:37:14,301
Ucinis li nesto divlje i
glupo. . .

1184
01:37:14,782 --> 01:37:16,581
. . .dokazat ces samo jedno.

1185
01:37:16,581 --> 01:37:18,142
A sto je to?

1186
01:37:20,182 --> 01:37:22,502
Da je on jedan sretan sin mora.

1187
01:37:28,583 --> 01:37:30,823
To je citat Charlieja Toschija.

1188
01:37:46,705 --> 01:37:49,225
Netko ce misliti da gore susis gace.

1189
01:37:54,506 --> 01:37:56,225
Lijepo izgledas.

1190
01:37:56,306 --> 01:37:57,986
Da, i to boli .

1191
01:38:25,109 --> 01:38:27,070
Prekrasan je, Garrete.

1192
01:38:28,109 --> 01:38:29,709
Hvala, Marta.

1193
01:38:31,710 --> 01:38:33,150
Sredi ih!

1194
01:38:38,910 --> 01:38:40,991
Sjajno uradjeno, Garrete.

1195
01:39:07,713 --> 01:39:09,314
Za Catherine.

1196
01:39:09,514 --> 01:39:11,114
Za Catherine.

1197
01:39:11,914 --> 01:39:13,674
Boze, zelim . . .

1198
01:39:16,715 --> 01:39:18,915
Zelim da je ona danas ovdje.

1199
01:39:23,915 --> 01:39:25,476
I svaki dan.

1200
01:41:03,886 --> 01:41:06,167
ata je rekao da si bila ondje.

1201
01:41:06,887 --> 01:41:08,847
Volio bih da sam znao.

1202
01:41:09,287 --> 01:41:11,487
Iznenadjenje. Glupa zamisao.

1203
01:41:12,287 --> 01:41:13,807
Ne, ja. . .

1204
01:41:14,087 --> 01:41:16,208
Drago mi je sto te vidim .

1205
01:41:18,288 --> 01:41:20,928
- Drago mi je sto si dosla.
- I meni .

1206
01:41:21,289 --> 01:41:23,488
Vidjela sam brod . Divan je.

1207
01:41:24,289 --> 01:41:25,649
Sjajan.

1208
01:41:26,689 --> 01:41:28,649
Drago mi je zbog tebe.

