01:42:52,499 --> 01:42:53,898
'Djenja.

1230
01:43:03,300 --> 01:43:05,260
Ne zelim te izgubiti .

1231
01:43:08,100 --> 01:43:09,420
Onda nemoj .

1232
01:43:26,462 --> 01:43:29,182
Zasto uvijek sjedis na istome mjestu?

1233
01:43:29,182 --> 01:43:30,982
