Nekad si sjedio ondje.

1237
01:43:53,785 --> 01:43:55,746
Daj decku salicu kave.

1238
01:44:02,786 --> 01:44:04,506
Izgledas grozno.

1239
01:44:06,386 --> 01:44:07,907
Dobro sam .

1240
01:44:08,787 --> 01:44:10,467
Pronasao si je?

