01:44:41,790 --> 01:44:42,990
Koji . . .

1250
01:44:42,990 --> 01:44:44,391
Chicago.

1251
01:44:44,790 --> 01:44:46,631
Tri minute. Nazovi .

1252
01:44:50,791 --> 01:44:52,952
To ti je posljednja prilika.

1253
01:45:02,793 --> 01:45:04,593
Dakako da je otisla.

1254
01:45:04,593 --> 01:45:06,272
Nije ona glupa.

1255
01:45:08,193 --> 01:45:09,393
Mislis da se zeli postaviti
izmedju tebe i . . .

1256
01:45:09,393 --> 01:45:12,394
- Ni meni nije sve jasno!
- A komu, do vraga, jest?

1257
01:45:12,394 --> 01:45:15,394
Mislis da mi je lako gledati
drugu zenu u tvojoj kuci?

1258
01:45:15,394 --> 01:45:16,994
Nije mi lako.

1259
01:45:17,194 --> 01:45:18,954
Reci cu ti jedno.

1260
01:45:19,594 --> 01:45:21,995
Dao bih milijun dolara
da vidim kako je grlis. . .

1261
01:45:21,995 --> 01:45:23,195
. . .i rjesavas sve putem .

1262
01:45:23,195 --> 01:45:24,395
Dosta o tome!

1263
01:45:24,395 --> 01:45:26,195
- Dosta?
- Da. Dosta!

1264
01:45:26,195 --> 01:45:27,635
Samo. . .

1265
01:45:30,396 --> 01:45:32,195
. . .zaboravi sve to.

1266
01:45:32,195 --> 01:45:33,596
Ne mogu!

1267
01:45:38,197 --> 01:45:40,077
Ne mogu zaboraviti !

1268
01:45:40,596 --> 01:45:42,437
Zasto, k vragu, ne?

1269
01:45:43,597 --> 01:45:45,397
Jer ti si moj sin.

1270
01:45:47,798 --> 01:45:50,078
- To se tebe ne tice.
- Molim?

1271
