Stisni saku.

1275
01:46:00,998 --> 01:46:02,399
Stisni !

1276
01:46:02,799 --> 01:46:04,439
Sad me udari !

1277
01:46:04,599 --> 01:46:06,840
Udari me u lice, pasji skote!

1278
01:46:10,000 --> 01:46:11,640
Ne tice me se?

1279
01:46:11,800 --> 01:46:13,760
Moj me se sin ne tice?

1280
01:46:14,800 --> 01:46:16,680
Sto drugo imam . . .

1281
01:46:18,401 --> 01:46:20,361
. . .sto mi je blisko?

1282
01:46:20,801 --> 01:46:22,761
ko je drugi ikad . . .

1283
01:46:23,202 --> 01:46:25,002
. . .stajao uz mene?

1284
01:46:25,002 --> 01:46:27,682
Mislis da ne poznajem tvoju bol?
Znam !

1285
01:46:28,002 --> 01:46:31,443
Ja sam odgovoran za dio nje.
Mislis da to mogu zaboraviti?

1286
01:46:33,402 --> 01:46:36,402
Kad je otisla u New York,
mogao si otici s njom . . .

1287
01:46:36,402 --> 01:46:38,803
. . .a ja sam bio ovdje.
Bolestan, pijan, na ledjima. . .

1288
01:46:38,803 --> 01:46:40,963
. . . unistavao sam i tebe.

1289
01:46:41,803 --> 01:46:44,604
Mozda je za vas dvoje
moglo biti drukcije.

1290
01:46:49,005 --> 01:46:51,084
Ja nisam ostao zbog tebe.

1291
01:46:52,005 --> 01:46:53,805
Ovo je ono sto jesam .

1292
01:46:53,805 --> 01:46:56,005
Ovo mjesto. Ovamo pripadam .

1293
01:46:57,405 --> 01:47:00,405
Ona se vratila jer je otkrila
da i ona ovamo pripada.

1294
01:47:00,405 --> 01:47:02,286
Izabrala je za sebe.

1295
01:47:05,205 --> 01:47:07,446
Boze, volio sam je zbog toga.

1296
01:47:08,806 --> 01:47:10,087
I ja.

1297
01:47:12,407 --> 01:47:14,687
Sad ti izaberi . Izaberi . . .

1298
01:47:14,806 --> 01:47:17,607
. . .izmedju jucer i sutra.
Izaberi jedno.

1299
01:47:19,607 --> 01:47:21,287
I ostani uz to!

