01:47:21,407 --> 01:47:23,368
A ja cu zavezati . . .

1301
01:47:23,808 --> 01:47:25,968
. . .i ostaviti te na miru.

1302
01:47:56,892 --> 01:47:59,292
" Uvijek ces znati gdje si . . .

1303
01:47:59,892 --> 01:48:01,772
. . .i gdje je dom .

1304
01:48:04,092 --> 01:48:05,892
Voli te heresa. "

