01:48:29,895 --> 01:48:31,616
Draga Catherine:

1306
01:49:04,699 --> 01:49:06,659
Ides na otvoreno more?

1307
01:49:07,699 --> 01:49:09,340
Da, gospodine.

1308
01:49:10,100 --> 01:49:12,060
Valjda znas sto radis.

1309
01:49:13,100 --> 01:49:14,820
Sve sam smislio.

1310
01:50:21,507 --> 01:50:23,067
Hej, stari .

1311
01:50:23,307 --> 01:50:25,268
Vrijeme je da ustanes.

1312
01:50:26,908 --> 01:50:28,548
Jos jedan dan.

1313
01:54:15,173 --> 01:54:17,533
Zovu ga Gradonacelnik 43. Ulice.

1314
01:54:18,173 --> 01:54:20,933
Sladak je. Svakoga poznaje.
Svima pomaze.

1315
01:54:22,374 --> 01:54:24,734
Bitno je da mu je 70. rodjendan.

1316
01:54:26,574 --> 01:54:29,455
Oprosti sto prekidam, heresa.
Poziv za tebe.

1317
01:54:29,574 --> 01:54:30,774
Mozes primiti poruku?

1318
01:54:30,774 --> 01:54:32,215
Hitno je.

1319
01:54:34,375 --> 01:54:35,575
Pardon.

1320
01:54:35,575 --> 01:54:37,375
Javi se u mom uredu.

1321
01:54:37,375 --> 01:54:38,775
Jase je?

1322
01:54:44,576 --> 01:54:46,256
Hej, djevojko?

1323
01:54:48,776 --> 01:54:50,256
Bolje. . .

1324
01:54:51,177 --> 01:54:53,697
. . .reci ovo dok jos mogu govoriti:

1325
01:54:55,978 --> 01:54:58,298
Na pucini je bio brod u nevolji.

1326
01:54:59,577 --> 01:55:01,458
Obitelj, njih troje.

1327
01:55:01,978 --> 01:55:03,939
Garret je pokusao. . .

1328
