01:55:35,582 --> 01:55:37,142
O, moj Boze!

1337
01:57:37,875 --> 01:57:39,595
Teska su vremena.

1338
01:57:39,675 --> 01:57:40,996
Udji .

1339
01:57:49,276 --> 01:57:51,397
Ovo sam pronasao na brodu.

