Ako ne. . .

1363
02:00:23,493 --> 02:00:25,894
. . .onda sam i dalje blagoslovljen
jer sam volio. . .

1364
02:00:25,894 --> 02:00:27,853
. . .dvaput u zivotu.

1365
02:00:28,294 --> 02:00:29,494
Ona mije to omogucila.

1366
02:00:29,494 --> 02:00:32,814
A ako ti kazem da je volim
koliko sam volio i tebe. . .

1367
02:00:33,094 --> 02:00:35,175
. . .onda ces sve znati.

1368
02:00:37,294 --> 02:00:39,535
Pocivaj u miru, ljubavi moja.

1369
02:00:39,695 --> 02:00:41,055
Garret.

